seo: Spring,漏洞检测,CVE-2018-1273,远程命令执行
summary: 该插件用于检测Spring Data Commons是否存在CVE-2018-1273远程命令执行漏洞，通过发送特定请求并验证响应来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the Spring Data Commons has the CVE-2018-1273 Remote Command Execution vulnerability by sending specific requests and verifying the response.
